---
// src/pages/disclaimer.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Disclaimer - MoneyInFuture"
  description="Important disclaimer: MoneyInFuture calculators are for educational and illustrative purposes only. They do not constitute financial, tax, or investment advice."
>
  <div class="calculator-header">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="calculator-description">Last updated: June 2026</p>
  </div>

  <section class="seo-content" style="max-width: 760px;">
    <h2>Not Financial Advice</h2>
    <p>All content, tools, and calculators on MoneyInFuture are provided <strong>for educational and illustrative
        purposes only</strong>. Nothing on this website constitutes financial advice, investment advice, tax
      advice, or any other type of professional advice. You should consult a registered financial advisor
      (SEBI-registered investment advisor or equivalent) before making any investment, tax, or financial planning
      decisions.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Accuracy of Calculations</h2>
    <p>While we strive to implement accurate financial formulas based on standard Indian investment conventions,
      the calculations on this site are based on <strong>assumed constant rates of return</strong> (CAGR).
      Real-world investments involve variable returns, market risk, credit risk, liquidity risk, and other factors
      that our calculators do not model. Actual results may differ materially from projections.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Tax Rules</h2>
    <p>Tax rates and exemptions shown (such as LTCG ₹1.25 lakh exemption, 12.5% LTCG, 20% STCG) are based on
      Indian tax rules as of the applicable financial year. Tax laws change frequently. MoneyInFuture does not
      guarantee that tax calculations are current or correct for your specific situation. Always verify with a
      qualified Chartered Accountant (CA) or tax professional.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">No Guarantee of Returns</h2>
    <p>Mutual fund investments and equity investments are subject to market risk. Past performance does not
      guarantee future results. The assumed return rates used in our calculators (e.g., 12% for equity SIPs) are
      illustrative only and may not be achievable.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>This site may link to external resources for reference. MoneyInFuture is not responsible for the content,
      accuracy, or privacy practices of any third-party website.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>MoneyInFuture and its operators shall not be liable for any financial loss, direct or indirect, arising
      from the use or reliance on any information, tool, or calculation provided on this website.</p>

    <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions or concerns, <a href="/contact.html">contact us here</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
